{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/understanding-uninitialized-variables","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Razumevanje Neinicijalizovanih Promenljivih","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada se JavaScript promenljive deklarisu, imaju pocetnu vrednost <code>undefined</code>. Ako uradite matematicku operaciju nad promenljivom koja je <code>undefined</code>, rezultat ce biti <code>NaN</code>, sto znaci <dfn>\"Not a Number\"</dfn>. Ako spojite string sa <code>undefined</code> promenljivom, dobicete string <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244aa","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Inicijalizujte tri promenljive <code>a</code>, <code>b</code> i <code>c</code> sa <code>5</code>, <code>10</code> i <code>\"I am a\"</code> redom, kako ne bi bile <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18335,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/understanding-uninitialized-variables"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Only change code below this line\nvar a;\nvar b;\nvar c;\n// Only change code above this line\n\na = a + 1;\nb = b + 5;\nc = c + \" String!\";","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>a</code> treba da bude deklarisana i da ima konacnu vrednost <code>6</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof a === 'number' && a === 6);"},{"text":"<p><code>b</code> treba da bude deklarisana i da ima konacnu vrednost <code>15</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof b === 'number' && b === 15);"},{"text":"<p><code>c</code> ne treba da sadrzi <code>undefined</code> i treba da ima konacnu vrednost stringa <code>I am a String!</code></p>","testString":"assert(!/undefined/.test(c) && c === 'I am a String!');"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da menjate kod ispod navedenog komentara.</p>","testString":"assert(\n  /a = a \\+ 1;/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)) &&\n    /b = b \\+ 5;/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)) &&\n    /c = c \\+ \" String!\";/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code))\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"understanding-uninitialized-variables","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/understanding-case-sensitivity-in-variables","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/declare-string-variables","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244aa","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/understanding-uninitialized-variables"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}